Company Overview of CIBC Trust Company (Bahamas) Limited



Snapshot People




Company Overview
CIBC Trust Company (Bahamas) Limited offers trust and fund administration services to private wealth management clients and institutional investors. The company was incorporated in 1973 and is based in Nassau, Bahamas. CIBC Trust Company (Bahamas) Limited operates as a subsidiary of CIBC Holdings (Cayman) Ltd. As of September 30, 2012, CIBC Trust Company (Bahamas) Limited operates as a subsidiary of FirstCaribbean International Bank Limited.


Goodman's Bay Corporate CentreWest Bay StreetNassau,  BahamasFounded in 1973



Phone: 242-356-1800

Fax: 242-322-3692








